Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:04.48,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Once, there was a Hero King
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:06.12,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,who brought peace to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:09.73,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,The Hero King herself, Adelaide-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:11.73,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,is going to tell us the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:13.74,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Let's listen, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:16.19,DogDays-main,Cu,0000,0000,0000,,Shinku and the others are late,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:20.19,DogDays-main,Cu,0000,0000,0000,,but let's get the story started!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:55.55,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Flognarde was once a place filled with
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:58.52,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,demons and dangerous wild animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:01.75,DogDays-main-top,A,0000,0000,0000,,The people lived in hiding to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:04.06,DogDays-ep-title-long,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,1)}Recollection: The Story of \Nthe Hero and the Princess
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:05.44,DogDays-main-top,A,0000,0000,0000,,escape these natural threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:08.51,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,There was one girl who wanted \Nto change this world:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.51,0:02:11.65,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,the princess of Pastillage, \Nback when it was still a monarchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:14.10,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The last king of Pastillage:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:16.14,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,the Hero Princess Clarifier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.14,0:02:17.32,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Fi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:21.32,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,But the Hero who she \Nsummoned was a noble girl
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:24.01,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,who'd been locked up in a corner \Nof the French countryside,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.01,0:02:26.37,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,with problems of her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:29.08,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:46.28,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised, and uncertain, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:49.60,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Hero Adelaide-sama, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:03:01.19,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:05.11,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I am the ruler of the Kingdom of Pastillage,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.37,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Clarifier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:17.66,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,And so I was taken to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.87,0:03:23.40,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,There are many dangerous \Ndemons in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:26.75,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,and the people cannot live \Ntheir lives in safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:30.93,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous even to travel on the roads,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:33.49,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,so the different countries
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:35.74,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,don't interact that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:38.49,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make this a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:40.69,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,better world for people to live in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:45.52,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I want to exterminate a lot of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:47.88,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,the demons to make our world bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:51.51,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I can't force the \Npeople and soldiers to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:54.80,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't think I should.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:58.53,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm planning on going on \Na trip to kill the demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:00.84,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You, personally?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:02.22,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:05.59,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to come with me, Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:09.60,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I've never fought any demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:12.28,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't know if I can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:13.48,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:18.61,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Pastillage has a divine weapon passed down \Nthrough the generations, "Gran Mars."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:22.50,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Hero, so you \Nshould be able to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:40.93,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure I understand how it works,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:42.88,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,but this gun is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:46.07,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get our guardian \Nequipment ready to go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:47.26,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:49.10,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,With this equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:52.07,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,you won't be hurt that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:01.00,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This looks kind of cool, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:06.17,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start going through the area \Naround the castle, little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:12.91,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Fi, are you really going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:14.43,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Valerie...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:16.29,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:18.35,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I've tried to stop you \Na lot of times already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:20.67,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I've told you to give up \Non fighting the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:23.03,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:26.82,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, this is what I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:36.06,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Hero, do you know Valerie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:39.97,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The first day I came here, he peeked \Non me when I was in the bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.93,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,That's not how it happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.93,0:05:45.29,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,You just happened to be in \Nthere during my bath time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.54,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:49.83,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,My little brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:51.12,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,the crown prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:54.39,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Valerie, this is the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.39,0:05:56.46,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,So she's the Hero, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:03.24,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Well, take good care of my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:08.89,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,If it gets dangerous, make sure you stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:12.85,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,And so their adventure began.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:14.77,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,The Hero Adel and Fi-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:17.42,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,set off all ready to go, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:25.09,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,That's them! The demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:27.66,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, they're cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:39.66,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,My clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:42.45,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,The guardian equipment protected us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:44.50,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Once it's all gone, we're in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:47.41,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:49.80,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Magic: Ruby Flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.29,0:07:17.11,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:24.16,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we fixed our equipment, now let's \Nfight the demons on the north side!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:26.05,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:36.93,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:52.35,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.35,0:07:53.41,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:57.63,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,And so, while it was hard at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:08:01.08,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,as we kept going, we got used \Nto fighting the demons
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:04.60,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,and we started being able to \Nfight powerful demons, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:12.11,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,This demon is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:14.50,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't lose here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:38.95,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, I'll let you handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:41.18,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Roger, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:10.61,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma Fuumetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.58,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Hina. Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:23.91,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.08,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,You girls okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:28.08,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:30.01,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,We just happened to be passing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:32.67,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,And we just happen to be very strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:43.10,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We're on a journey looking \Nfor certain katanas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:44.48,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You saw one back there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:49.10,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that was sticking out of that local \Nmole god is called a "cursed blade."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:53.36,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Creatures and local gods that touch a \Ncursed blade transform into demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:55.48,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The goal of our journey is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:58.55,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,to find them and seal them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:02.60,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,And part of that job is saving \Nthe creatures and local gods
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:04.62,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,who touched them and turned into demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:07.79,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Um, would the two of you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:10.13,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,please meet my little brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:14.00,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Cursed blades, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:15.88,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I know them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:18.27,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,And I know where they are, mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.27,0:10:19.51,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:23.39,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I research the history of \Nthe demons and this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:27.02,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to wipe out the demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.32,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:31.75,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,find all the cursed blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:35.78,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,There are people having trouble because \Nof the demons all over right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:39.28,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,I want to save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.93,0:10:42.68,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a hypothetical, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:45.12,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Right now the demons are a big threat,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:47.82,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,and the different countries don't really \Ncome into contact with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:52.04,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, there's neither the opportunity \Nnor the time for humans to fight each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:55.36,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,But if the demons were \Nwiped out and the world
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:58.48,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,was at peace, what do \Nyou think would happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:02.08,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Then humans would start fighting each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:06.43,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Peaceful areas. Fertile areas. \NThe best roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:09.31,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,They would start fighting \Nover who controls them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:13.81,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I think we're best \Noff the way things are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:17.01,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I think we might be better off
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:19.32,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,just protecting our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:22.43,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That might be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.06,0:11:26.07,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,It's the job of a king or a ruler to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.07,0:11:28.09,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,keep the people from fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:30.86,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, we have to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:33.21,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,keep finding the cursed blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:37.95,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Fi and Adel are going to continue \Ntheir journey to fight the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:40.89,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,So it would make sense \Nfor us to go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:45.76,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,So it would be really helpful \Nif you told us more about
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:48.23,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,the cursed blades and the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:52.23,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,You're a really simplistic kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:54.36,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a kid! My name's Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:56.61,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,And you didn't listen to what I just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:57.98,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,I did so!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:12:00.60,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Would you come with us, Valerie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:02.02,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:05.62,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually a little opposed \Nto his coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:11.62,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Hina and I lost our home to demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.05,0:12:15.58,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,When that happened, we both \Nwere soaked in demon blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.25,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably why
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:20.38,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,she and I both can't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:24.30,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Hina hasn't grown at all since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:27.14,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:30.02,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much we don't \Nknow about the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:32.64,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know what might happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:34.88,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Do the princess and the Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:38.40,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,still want to continue their journey anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:44.08,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:47.31,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get rid of the threat of the demons\Nso we can broaden our horizons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:50.20,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make everyone in the world smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:51.70,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Adel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:54.86,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know much about
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:57.10,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,this world, or the demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:13:01.52,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,but I love the people who \Nlive on this continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:05.88,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,And more than anything I love Fi-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:07.88,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,the princess who called me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:11.68,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help her wish come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:13.31,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.44,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,satisfied with being her gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:20.24,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to do whatever she decides.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:23.14,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:27.07,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, if there's anything \Ndangerous or bad she tries to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:28.83,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure to stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:30.30,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:32.55,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,You heard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:34.03,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do, Valerie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:38.21,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,You've made it sound like I don't \Nhave a choice, you stupid kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:39.71,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:43.46,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,And so we now had five members in our party:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:47.30,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,The traveling swordsmith and \Nanti-magic user, Isuca,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.61,0:13:48.72,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,and the sword master, Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:52.10,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,Valerie, the demon researcher, \Nand the princess, Fi,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:55.41,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,and the Hero, Adel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:09.58,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,We would defeat the demons \Nto liberate towns and roads,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:13.49,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,and help countries that \Nwere hurt by the demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:16.06,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,bringing nation and nation together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:20.04,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,We spent a long time traveling \Nover deserts, volcanoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:24.51,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,and the ends of glaciers, \Nall over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:30.89,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,We fought Kleitos, the descendant \Nof the True Dragons,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:33.77,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,and afterwards became his friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:36.38,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,And we became stronger after
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:40.23,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,the creation of my Hero Crystal \Nand Fi's spirit crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:44.56,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,We went all the way above the clouds to find
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:47.38,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,a legendary blade that could seal demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:51.06,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,This is a big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:54.52,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let's go, Adel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:56.08,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Valerie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:05.63,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,At some point, we became famous enough
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:08.87,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,that we were known all around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:12.47,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,We defeated over 2,000 demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:14.97,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,and Valerie's research advanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:17.24,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,Many roads were opened,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:20.68,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,and the various nations began \Nto interact with one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:24.55,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,The people's lives became much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:26.88,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,Around this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:30.11,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,wars between humans began to start,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:33.91,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,but the princess put \Ntogether an organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:38.27,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,This organization established rules \Ngoverning wars between nations:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:40.16,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,the Continental Treaty Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:43.71,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's a symbol of Flognarde's peace
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:46.11,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,that continues to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:48.80,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,That's a wonderful story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:49.93,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:53.18,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,So our ancestors lived through \Na time like that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:56.40,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, that was when people
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:15:58.93,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,stopped seeing the researcher, Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:01.44,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Why was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:05.31,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I had to continue my \Nresearch into demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:08.00,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,For research purposes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:10.57,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I raised and kept lots of demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:14.21,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,And so I decided it would \Nbe more convenient to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:16.83,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,call myself a Demon King and go underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.48,0:16:19.87,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I'd started being a Demon King as a joke,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:22.83,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,but eventually I started \Nto get really into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:29.67,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Playing with people who'd heard the rumors \Nof the Demon King and come to defeat him
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:34.36,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,and teaching rulers who'd \Nforgotten about the threat of
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:37.80,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,the demons and dragons and \Ngotten a little too cocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:42.10,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the research of \Nthe Demon King Valerie,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:43.69,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,I um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:46.36,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to grow up,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:49.36,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:54.52,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,But even after the world was at peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.21,0:16:58.12,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Fi kept up her journey to defeat the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:02.14,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's retire from demon hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:06.38,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You have your job as a king to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.72,0:17:10.35,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You've had me handle all your \Ngovernment duties lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:13.38,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:16.14,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:19.64,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to take care of Pastillage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:21.99,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:25.16,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I called you here for \Nmy own selfish reasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:29.32,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't even send you back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:33.40,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I've always regretted that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:37.77,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I've told you this many times before...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:40.30,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,There's nobody back home
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:43.29,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,who'll be sad or bothered if I'm gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:46.30,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy I was able to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:48.67,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,come here, and be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:51.28,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to help everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:53.42,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,to be called a Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:56.15,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,to be surrounded by people's smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.21,0:17:59.70,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you called me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:03.46,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you were
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:05.93,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,courageous enough to stay by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:08.77,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy when
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:10.59,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,you said you'd be my gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:14.23,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,But from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:18.70,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to live your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.46,0:18:22.09,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'd had a feeling this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:26.95,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,Fi was a user of spirit and healing magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:30.17,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,which made her especially vulnerable \Nto the poison the demons put out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:33.10,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,The morning after we'd spoken,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.12,0:18:37.48,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,she left like always...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:40.40,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,There was no sign of her for two weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:43.72,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,and then she showed up barely able to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:51.41,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:54.90,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,She'd defeated a demon possessed by \Na cursed blade in Northern Villand,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:58.46,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,the Poison Dragon of the \NIce Wall, all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:01.39,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,She went to sleep, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:05.43,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,Valerie told me that during our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:08.05,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,Fi had realized how much longer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:10.32,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,she had to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.47,0:19:19.23,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'd stayed put,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.23,0:19:22.26,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have lasted that much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:26.10,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I decided I'd rather keep going towards
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:28.36,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,the world I dreamed of,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:33.27,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,instead of quitting my journey midway and \Nextending my life for no good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:35.78,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,And just like I'd dreamed of,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.78,0:19:38.14,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,the world is so much bigger now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:41.19,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to help the world take
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:43.08,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,a step closer towards peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:47.51,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I don't regret it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:49.37,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:51.75,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:56.59,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,And so
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:20:01.39,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,the Hero Princess, Clarifier Einz \NPastillage, went into a long slumber,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:04.08,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,never to be forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:07.06,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,in the history of Flognarde.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:11.84,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,Pastillage became a dukedom
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.84,0:20:13.81,DogDays-narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,instead of a monarchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:14.58,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.58,0:20:17.01,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Valerie and I slowly began to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:19.32,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,disappear from the people's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:22.82,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,We watched the children who were \Nborn set out on their own,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:25.32,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,and then watched our \Ngrandchildren be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:29.83,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,After that, we decided to sleep \Nin the same place Fi did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:34.67,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Isuka and Hina have continued \Ntheir journey ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.47,0:20:38.59,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,I met Yukikaze after
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:41.09,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,my brother and I split up to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:43.36,DogDays-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,continue our journeys separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:53.92,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,And when Shinku and Couver \Ntouched the monument,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:56.56,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,we awoke, and that's how \Nwe got where we are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:59.57,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to see that our \Ndescendants are doing well,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:02.00,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,and the world is at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:03.68,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,We're happy, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.68,0:21:06.07,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm sure Fi is, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.67,0:21:10.58,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,But of course, the current peace \Nisn't going to last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:13.33,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,There's no guarantee
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:16.08,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,that a Hero will come\Nsave you when you fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:19.78,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to not forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.85,0:21:21.66,DogDays-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:25.46,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,This ended up taking a lot of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:27.34,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:29.07,DogDays-main,Co,0000,0000,0000,,Bring some more tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:31.60,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:33.35,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,We're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:37.35,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is the story...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:39.36,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:41.30,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You three are so late!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:44.17,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've told Millihiore and Shinku
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.17,0:21:46.85,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,a little of it before...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:52.72,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The Heroes and the \Nprincesses are all happy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:57.84,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Please keep watching over us, Fi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:34.71,DogDays-main-top,A,0000,0000,0000,,My ancestor's story was so moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.71,0:23:37.85,DogDays-main-top,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still watching over the \Nhappiness of my descendants.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:40.09,DogDays-next-ep-title,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,1)}The Star Whale\Nin the Sky Sea
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.85,0:23:39.74,DogDays-main-top,A,0000,0000,0000,,See you next time, too, okay?
